text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This transmits obsolete IRM 25.7.7, Exempt Organizations/Business Master File Handbook (EO/BMF), EO/BMF Reports.

The material relating to Exempt Organizations/Business Master File Handbook (EO/BMF), Section 7, EO/BMF Reports previously contained in IRM section 25.7.7 is incorporated into IRM 25.7.1, starting at IRM 25.7.1.18, continuing through IRM 25.7.1.19.
This supersedes and obsoletes IRM 25.7.7, Exempt Organizations/Business Master File Handbook (EO/BMF), EO/BMF Reports, dated January 1, 2018.
Jennifer A. Jett Director, Business Systems Planning Shared Services Tax Exempt and Government Entities
